# Smart Attendance System (Java)

Face recognition-based attendance system using Java and OpenCV.

## Features
- Register students via webcam
- Recognize faces and mark attendance automatically
- Attendance stored in CSV (attendance.csv)
- Simple GUI with Swing

## Requirements
- Java 8+
- OpenCV 4+ (with Java bindings)
- Haar cascade XML file (haarcascade_frontalface_alt.xml)

## Usage
1. Place OpenCV JARs in lib/ and configure in IDE.
2. Run Main.java.
3. Click "Register Student" to add students.
4. Click "Mark Attendance" to start recognition.
